window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Peace is not the human way.</b></p> <p>War stirs in the distance, out of the edges of thought. Trouble brews through the land even though a great evil has been quelled.</p> <p>Garek is a traitor to his kind. A minotaur that has given up war. An example must be set. A horde marches for these lands to claim his life.</p> <p>Through this all, the farm grows. The attention of many is on this new God-slayer, and they find not a great adventurer, but a farmer, content in his ways. The Gods Above are not pleased with contention.</p> <p>They demand entertainment.</p>"; 
